{"tid":2513796,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢草莓音樂節變無罩大會　逾萬人「零設防」狂歡","createTime":"2021-05-02T22:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T22:48:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"21a797800bceb151fc976a3e1cb7b2622ef98a30","tid":2513796,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:09:36.000Z","msg":"中國「五一」連續假期處處出現人潮聚集，最先爆出疫情的湖北武漢市，舉辦大型露天「草莓音樂節」，現場擠進成千上萬的人潮，且許多人沒有戴口罩，形同對疫情不設防，大會雖宣稱採取分區入場措施，但現場人擠人的情況還是挺嚇人。有媒體擔心，若現場爆發群聚感染，恐使疫情急劇惡化。<br />\n<br />\n中國多個大城市趁「五一」長假，舉行多場草莓音樂節，去年因應疫情改為線上舉辦，今年回歸實體現場演唱。在微博流傳大量草莓音樂節照片，大部份參與者都沒戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n1日在武漢舉行的演唱會，主辦方宣稱，現場人數都有受到限制，大約有1.1萬人入場，場內採取分區隔離，每個區域只讓一定數量民眾內進。<br />\n<br />\n不過，現場照片見到絕大多數人完全沒遮蓋口鼻。居住在武漢的23歲學生透露，去年當地爆發疫情，大家付出巨大努力才有如今的防疫成就，能夠來到音樂節現場，他感到很開心。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，這次是武漢在去年年初爆發疫情後首個大型公開音樂活動。去年8月正當疫情在全球蔓延之際，武漢瑪雅海灘水上樂園也曾舉行音樂會，數以千計的男女身穿泳裝參與，當時也沒人佩戴口罩。他們在游泳池裏嬉戲，隨着音樂節拍載歌載舞，完全感覺不到當地曾有大量的染疫死亡個案發生。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210503/LP2GV5KC7BDNRAQTOGLF6DNVVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210503%2FLP2GV5KC7BDNRAQTOGLF6DNVVY%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=a5572a9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210503%2FLP2GV5KC7BDNRAQTOGLF6DNVVY%2F&h=a12f952a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210503/LP2GV5KC7BDNRAQTOGLF6DNVVY/</a>"},{"pid":"99d115c0e8b8c09652e623395ffaee240ffe1a11","tid":2513796,"uid":308107,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都想狂歡啊"},{"pid":"69b4da4125b7f739dcc3326b426f561a81fb6ade","tid":2513796,"uid":234089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:12:51.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩 偉一祖國話佢哋唔會有確診 就算有都係外國傳入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依堆人就好 準備做外國人"},{"pid":"eda1b7f0a32156a2837f4f9ddda960142c2c8741","tid":2513796,"uid":54256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:16:47.000Z","msg":"笑完印度點火<br />\n話唔定遲啲到返佢地點火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944e34a18d528a2f31f2b661f530356b09039f86","tid":2513796,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:18:33.000Z","msg":"正常生活?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae669a658d84093407ca82feda12d9282056f7b","tid":2513796,"uid":227062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:20:04.000Z","msg":"以為無套大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3140ff205121ce1a34a1398ddf06928c5d1c7d","tid":2513796,"uid":119485,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:20:26.000Z","msg":"國內朋友已經可以正常生活<br />\n中國疫情處理真係No 1"},{"pid":"a7d529e4f155882d2d9b12485d30567ff787b1e7","tid":2513796,"uid":252920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:27:09.000Z","msg":"支那都無香港政府咁撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71531ea85aef23152a4ca412afaa9e17cd231d3","tid":2513796,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:44:26.000Z","msg":"來港易"},{"pid":"5ba5bcd575edb19c9c50a94d397b9ad07830f8ba","tid":2513796,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eda1b7f0a32156a2837f4f9ddda960142c2c8741","tid":2513796,"uid":54256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:16:47.000Z","msg":"笑完印度點火<br />\n話唔定遲啲到返佢地點火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:48:25.000Z","msg":"武漢再次點火"}]}